### Football League Management API Examples

### 1. Get all leagues
GET http://localhost:8080/api/leagues
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get league by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/leagues/1
Accept: application/json

### 3. Create new league
POST http://localhost:8080/api/leagues
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bundesliga",
  "country": "Germany",
  "season": 2024
}

### 4. Update league
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/leagues/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Premier League Updated",
  "country": "England",
  "season": 2024
}

### 5. Get all teams
GET http://localhost:8080/api/teams
Accept: application/json

### 6. Get teams by league
GET http://localhost:8080/api/teams/league/1
Accept: application/json

### 7. Create new team
POST http://localhost:8080/api/teams
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Arsenal",
  "city": "London",
  "foundedYear": 1886,
  "stadium": "Emirates Stadium",
  "leagueId": 1
}

### 8. Get all players
GET http://localhost:8080/api/players
Accept: application/json

### 9. Get players by team
GET http://localhost:8080/api/players/team/1
Accept: application/json

### 10. Get top scorers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/players/top-scorers?minGoals=10
Accept: application/json

### 11. Create new player
POST http://localhost:8080/api/players
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bukayo Saka",
  "age": 22,
  "position": "Winger",
  "jerseyNumber": 7,
  "nationality": "English",
  "teamId": 1,
  "statistics": {
    "goals": 12,
    "assists": 8,
    "yellowCards": 1,
    "redCards": 0,
    "matchesPlayed": 18
  }
}

### 12. Update player statistics
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/players/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Erling Haaland",
  "age": 24,
  "position": "Striker",
  "jerseyNumber": 9,
  "nationality": "Norwegian",
  "teamId": 1,
  "statistics": {
    "goals": 30,
    "assists": 6,
    "yellowCards": 2,
    "redCards": 0,
    "matchesPlayed": 25
  }
}

### 13. Get players by position
GET http://localhost:8080/api/players/position/Striker
Accept: application/json

### 14. Get players by nationality
GET http://localhost:8080/api/players/nationality/Spanish
Accept: application/json

### 15. Get players by age range
GET http://localhost:8080/api/players/age-range?minAge=20&maxAge=30
Accept: application/json

### 16. Delete player
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/players/1

### 17. Delete team
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/teams/1

### 18. Delete league
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/leagues/1

### 19. Check if league exists
GET http://localhost:8080/api/leagues/1/exists
Accept: application/json

### 20. Count teams in league
GET http://localhost:8080/api/teams/league/1/count
Accept: application/json
